The rounding mode to use for arbitrary precision arithmetic on
numbers, by default \fB"N"\fR (IEEE-754 roundTiesToEven mode).
See
.I https://www.gnu.org/software/gawk/manual/html_node/Setting-the-rounding-mode
for the details.
